node.text:
Hannah Walker @spannawalker speaks to 3 x World Champion and 3 x Paralympic Medallist, @denise_schindler to recap day 11 of the Olympic Games, speaking about @lisabrennauer @lisaklein157 @franzibrausse @mieke.kroeger becoming Olympic Champions in the women’s team pursuit, Netherlands becoming Olympic Champions in the team sprint and all the action from the men’s team pursuit as well as what to expect from the Paralympic Games in 20 days!

#Tokyo2020 #Olympics

node.title: Tokyo Talk Show 🇯🇵 Day Eleven Recap with Hannah Walker and Denise Schindl

node.text:
Hannah Walker @spannawalker speaks to 3 x World Champion and 3 x Paralympic Medallist, @denise_schindler to recap day 11 of the Olympic Games, speaking about @lisabrennauer @lisaklein157 @franzibrausse @mieke.kroeger becoming Olympic Champions in the women’s team pursuit, Netherlands becoming Olympic Champions in the team sprint and all the action from the men’s team pursuit as well as what to expect from the Paralympic Games in 20 days!

#Tokyo2020 #Olympics
